summary: Puts an monastery grounds,in Falkreath hold.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ffffff][size=3]Puts an monastery grounds,in Falkreath hold.
Beneath the Guardian stones,is an kinda like High Hrothgar,but for women monastery.
There are two "nuns" - Diana and Haelga.
And monastery has two areas : the Living Quarters,and the Garden Area.
Kind like five in H.Hrothgar,so is only two here.[/size][/color][/font]
